Details.JobSummary:
About the Position: Positions are within U.S. Army Corps of Engineers, Phila Dist Off, Ops Div, Reg Br with duty Stations in Phila, PA; Gouldsboro, PA, & Dover, DE. Positions are temporary not to exceed one year, may be extended up to 5 years, and may be made permanent without further competition. This is an Interdisciplinary position which may be filled under any of the following:
Geographer, 0150;
Biologist, 0401;
Environmental Engineer, 819; or
Physical Scientist, 1301

